title: jm13853211
author: jm13853211
pages:
#- I have agreed to purchase the spider spawners for 2d from Hopsoplo under the terms that I will not destroy them and will attempt to make a decent looking structure or grinder with them. Furthermore I agree that I will not attempt to sell the spawners 
#- without Hopsoplo's consent, and that if I wish to relinquish ownership of these spawners, I may do so, but under the knowledge I will not receive my d back.
The spawners in question are the trio located near the university of Aurora,
#- though for security reasons their exact location has not been disclosed. Most importantly, Hopsoplo does not have the right to interfere with or take back these spawners unless I breach one of the rules listed in this contract. If I destroy the spawners 
#- or sell them to someone else without
Hopsoplo's consent, I agree to pay reperations of 5d. Any profits that I make off of these spawners are mine and mine alone, and I do not have to give them to Hopsoplo or anyone else unless a breach
#- of rules happens. By signing this contract, I agree to all these terms and show my understanding that this contract is under the protection of the law and will be handled as such.
#- 